'''Štěpán Chaloupek''' (born 8 March 2003) is a Czech professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defender (association football)|defender]] for [[SK Slavia Prague|Slavia Prague]] and the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic national team]].

==Life==
Chaloupek was born in [[Meziboří]].<ref name=denik>{{cite web |last=Novotný|first=Vladimír|title=Teplický milionový obchod jde už do finále. Chaloupek se stane posilou Slavie|url=https://teplicky.denik.cz/fotbal-prvni-liga/teplicky-milionovy-obchod-jde-uz-do-finale-chaloupek-se-stane-posilou-slavie-202.html|work=Deník.cz|language=cs|date=2023-11-29|access-date=2025-02-21}}</ref>

==Club career==
Chaloupek started with football in his hometown Meziboří.<ref name=slavia>{{cite web |title=Štěpán Chaloupek přestupuje do Slavie|url=https://www.slavia.cz/article/21345-Stepan-Chaloupek-prestupuje-do-Slavie|publisher=SK Slavia Prague|language=cs|date=2024-01-05|access-date=2025-02-21}}</ref> He was then raised in [[FK Teplice|Teplice]], where he was captain of the under-19 team.<ref name=denik/>

He made his debut in senior football in the [[2021–22 Czech Cup|2021–22 season of the Czech Cup]] in August 2021. In the [[Czech First League]], he debuted for Teplice in November 2021, in their 4–2 away loss against [[AC Sparta Prague|Sparta Prague]]. In the [[2022–23 Czech First League|2022–23]] season, he became a stable member of the starting line-up.<ref name=slavia/>

In January 2024, it was announced that Chaloupek signed a four-year contract with [[SK Slavia Prague|Slavia Prague]], effective from 30 June 2024.<ref name=slavia/> After the [[2023–24 Czech First League|2023–24]] season, Chaloupek won the award for Teplice's best player of the season.<ref>{{cite web |title=Sklářem roku se stal Štěpán Chaloupek|url=https://fkteplice.cz/article/11336-Sklarem-roku-se-stal-Stepan-Chaloupek-|publisher=FK Teplice|language=cs|date=2024-05-28|access-date=2025-02-21}}</ref>

==International career==
Chaloupek played for the [[Czech Republic national under-21 football team|Czech Republic U21 team]]. In the [[2025 UEFA European Under-21 Championship qualification]], he played almost all of the matches in the starting line-up, helping the team to qualify for [[2025 UEFA European Under-21 Championship|2025 UEFA Euro U21]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Štěpán Chaloupek|url=https://www.fotbal.cz/repre/hrac/hraci/16334359|publisher=[[Football Association of the Czech Republic]]|language=cs|access-date=2025-02-21}}</ref>

In November 2025, Chaloupek debuted for the senior [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic national team]] in a match against [[Gibraltar national football team|Gibraltar]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Známkování: Příjemný konec bídné kvalifikace. Jedničkáři ze Slavie, zarazil nulový Schick|url=https://www.sport.cz/clanek/fotbal-ms-znamkovani-prijemny-konec-bidne-kvalifikace-jednickari-ze-slavie-zarazil-nulovy-schick-5285240|work=Sport.cz|language=cs|date=2025-11-17|access-date=2026-01-22}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Among his strengths are one-on-one duels, head play and constructive passing.<ref name=slavia/>

